{"tid":1630436,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【留意】唔頒下禁制令嘅真正原因","createTime":"2019-10-06T12:30:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T13:02:20.000Z","uid":173207,"like":21,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"5b93a9aa370449e76feed075c822da2b5dac1221","tid":1630436,"uid":173207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:30:14.000Z","msg":"Guys, pls have a read of the following:<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-<br />\n小心被帶風向！唔好理解錯法官唔頒禁制令原因，同我傳開去！<br />\n<br />\n見到好多post鬧法官唔頒禁制令，誤解判詞話因為法庭唔信蒙面法會令示威者行動升級，所以要做俾法庭睇。<br />\n<br />\n但法庭其實完全冇講過啲咁嘅野。 (利申: law撚, 喺法庭現場)<br />\n<br />\n其實個官基本上係講：<br />\n<br />\n1. 根據案例，除非被覆核嘅條例好好好明顯地違憲，法庭唔會喺正式覆核前頒臨時禁制令。詳見：梁頌恆案para 13：<a href=\"http://www.hklii.hk/cgi-bin/sinodisp/eng/hk/cases/hkcfi/2018/1869.html?stem=&amp;synonyms=&amp;query=(2018%205%20HKC%20138\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hklii.hk%2Fcgi-bin%2Fsinodisp%2Feng%2Fhk%2Fcases%2Fhkcfi%2F2018%2F1869.html%3Fstem%3D%26synonyms%3D%26query%3D%282018%25205%2520HKC%2520138&d=5qKB33MXKEG0NT2XrWEv6s04bh6pArHnk2fwDmvpgUU%3D&h=1255f011\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.hklii.hk/cgi-bin/sinodisp/eng/hk/cases/hkcfi/2018/1869.html?stem=&amp;synonyms=&amp;query=(2018%205%20HKC%20138</a>)%20OR%20ncotherjcitationtitles(2018%205%20HKC%20138)<br />\n<br />\n2. 呢次審訊只係關乎臨時禁制令，而申請人未有獲得法庭司法覆核嘅許可 (因為司法覆核嘅許可星期二先審)，而根據Practice Direction SL3 第10段，法庭一般都唔會係呢個階段頒臨時禁制令。詳見PD SL3, para 10：<a href=\"https://legalref.judiciary.hk/lrs/common/pd/pdcontent.jsp?pdn=PDSL3.htm&amp;lang=CH\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Flegalref.judiciary.hk%2Flrs%2Fcommon%2Fpd%2Fpdcontent.jsp%3Fpdn%3DPDSL3.htm%26lang%3DCH&d=5qKB33MXKEG0NT2XrWEv6s04bh6pArHnk2fwDmvpgUU%3D&h=7f0d189f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://legalref.judiciary.hk/lrs/common/pd/pdcontent.jsp?pdn=PDSL3.htm&amp;lang=CH</a><br />\n<br />\n3. 因此，雖然法庭初步認為司法覆核有得拗，但現階段都唔會頒臨時禁制令。<br />\n<br />\n由此可以見到個官冇(未)講過條例有冇問題，亦冇睇死手足唔會升級，而最早下星期先開始討論緊急法同禁蒙面法違唔違憲，搞法庭對我地冇好處，只會：<br />\n<br />\n1. 令我地失去外國戰線: 班外國人權法治撚會覺得我地同班popo同港共政府一樣，唔尊重法治；<br />\n<br />\n2. 令抗爭內部分化: 唔少手足對法庭有情意結，搞法庭未必人人支持。<br />\n<br />\n我好奇怪點解冇一份新聞有講裁決理由 (可能班記者聽唔明)。如果有人亂咁喺度帶風向，成件事就好危險。所以小弟奉勸大家：千祈，千祈，千祈唔好俾人誤導，唔好衝動行事！<br />\n<br />\n最後想帶出一個重點: 我地冇輸到，因為個官都有提過呢單司法覆核有得拗，只係唔係今日拗！<br />\n<br />\n留意郭榮鏗同長毛都會幫手入稟JR，大家唔好自亂陣腳<br />\n<br />\n更多法律分析及實用錦囊<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/hkwarroom\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkwarroom&d=5qKB33MXKEG0NT2XrWEv6s04bh6pArHnk2fwDmvpgUU%3D&h=866fe25a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkwarroom</a><br />\nBy 個腦生左係屎忽度<br />\n<br />\n<del></del><br />\nSource:毛EE FB<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/548856635131690/posts/3013508221999840?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F548856635131690%2Fposts%2F3013508221999840%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=5qKB33MXKEG0NT2XrWEv6s04bh6pArHnk2fwDmvpgUU%3D&h=3916e53b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/548856635131690/posts/3013508221999840?sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"7b049edfe0e3ac4426eb9b98e0aa03d779fd6430","tid":1630436,"uid":130079,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:31:02.000Z","msg":"［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630201\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630201</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現時連登急需亦好要一個<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">英文台/或者係新既英文介面，全部台都有英文版咁。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n主要用途係對外文宣用，如果個論壇冧左，<span style=\"color: purple;\">外國人更加清楚lihkg被攻擊同香港自由被剝既嚴重性</span>。<br />\n<br />\ntwitter有lihkg,reddit開post<br />\n但始終都唔係lihkg開英文台<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好處：<br />\n1.連登多左流覽量，廣告費多左<br />\n2.同上，每次被攻擊都睇到香港無自由，the world is watching<br />\n3.理論上少風向文宣，因為如果要落手帶風向，對家就要大學畢業既人，文宣戰立即少左散仔協會參戰，但香港市民最多就係呢一堆人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家如果見到既<br />\n幫手：<br />\n1.<span style=\"color: red;\">幫推，唔該3連推一次</span><br />\n2.連登search其他 英文台 國際台，<span style=\"color: green;\">將入面相關要求既post再推</span><br />\n<br />\n3.share link去fb tg，叫其他有account既人入黎再一齊做返1同2<br />\n4.<span style=\"color: orange;\">堅持每日全部post再一推</span><br />\n5.Fb 連登到留comment，叫連仔開英文台<br />\n6. Fb進行洗版式接龍活動，令到連仔開到/知道要開英文台為止<br />\n7.太舊既post只可以推番三個上水，幫手推埋thx<br />\n<br />\n如果你係要求開英文台post樓主既：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">集中連推自己所有既英文台post，我會幫推，唔好放棄推<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"ac684f14fc38560c0cd467ed2c0691a8df5cfe3f","tid":1630436,"uid":190464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:32:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b4d5335b861b71fa82c1b555ad04c126789370e7","tid":1630436,"uid":19437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:33:27.000Z","msg":"港共你越挑釁我我越唔中你計<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7b915fd8b9b6c79a6cf9676f447920c3aa93aa7","tid":1630436,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:33:47.000Z","msg":"【行動】盡快整理所有警暴片段，同納粹暴行做對比，爭取西方實際行動支持香港<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1628720\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1628720</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n請幫手推文支持<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1628720\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1628720</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"3cc9a961d2b8c486fe5477f4f5660f9b09b6ba45","tid":1630436,"uid":157462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:36:37.000Z","msg":"推比啲唔識law嘅連登仔睇清楚"},{"pid":"6b0c2052d5cdd5422f8a8ca31dc6a05568525c24","tid":1630436,"uid":303862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:38:42.000Z","msg":"法律野就留返法律人做<br />\n各自努力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0be321415d0002c67239a81e147969030744ff5","tid":1630436,"uid":212003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:39:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"078956d4172975541d53b6611854a6caf77b9c12